      <title>2023 年洪水造成数千人死亡后利比亚监禁 12 名官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/libya-jails-12-officials-after-2023-floods-that-killed-thousands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，利比亚发生毁灭性的洪水，造成数千人死亡，随后利比亚一家法院判处了 12 名参与管理该国东部水坝的人员监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/libya-jails-12-officials-after-2023-floods-that-killed-thousands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:15:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
